# .cursorrules — shaked-wg-agent

## Session startup
1. Read `_aos/roadmap.yaml`
2. Read `_aos/context/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`
3. Read `_aos/context/ACTIVATION_ARCH.md`

## Data authority
- Local domain data remains in app/data files.
- For DB-backed AOS governance workflows, structured AOS state mutates via API + `deploy_cascade()` (ADR034).

## Validation
- Run `bash _aos/lean-kit/modules/validation-quality/scripts/validate_aos.sh .` before gate claims.
